| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1821 — Recovery Inhibition (monti)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 867edee0-5dfd-54bc-8b3c-8c13398834c1"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
